Method credit
-------------
This pack implements the method described in:
  "VideoMaMa: Mask-Guided Video Matting via Generative Prior" (CVPR 2026),
  cvlab-kaist — https://github.com/cvlab-kaist/VideoMaMa
The method, the original reference code, and the trained weights are the work of
those authors. This project re-implements the (published) inference method using
the standard `diffusers` API and adds its own windowing / focus-crop tooling.

